---
title: Tous les articles
date: 2020-08-05
description: The Posts List display is controled in /src/_data/structure.js and ships with 4 options.
layout: page
eleventyNavigation:
  key: main
  title: Textes
  order: 1    # order to display in the nav
seo:
  title: Tous les articles
  description:
pagination:
  data: collections.publishedPosts
  size: 40
  alias: posts
  reverse: true
postListItemStyle:
  complete: true
  showPagination: true

---

<div class="blog-wrapper">
<span class="mb-3 label sm-text"><a class="underline" href="https://observablehq.com/@xenomachina/truchet-tiles-variant-intertwined-quarter-circles"> Source du code</a> générant les images de vignette par défaut. </span>

  <form class="search " id="search-form" aria-controls="post-list">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:w-1/2 field">
      <label for="searchField" class="label">Rechercher</label>
      <div class="relative">
        <input type="search"  class="w-full p-2 border-gray-600 rounded-md " placeholder="" id="searchField"/>
        <input type="image" name="submit" src="/assets/UI/search.svg" border="0" class="absolute h-10 p-2 right-2">
      </div>
    </div>
    <p id="noResultsFound" class="py-4 text-base" style="display: none" role="alert">
      Aucun résultat.
    </p>
  </form>
  {% set postslist = posts %}

  {% include 'components/postslist.njk' %}

  <div class=" lg:container-wide">
    <hr class="my-8">

    <h3 class"text-gray-700">Tous les thèmes</h3>
    {% set tags = collections.tagList %}
    {% include "components/tagpills.njk" %}
  </div>
</div>
<script  src="/assets/scripts/{{hashes_js['search.js']}}" defer></script>